fields.title: Nasus' Statue
fields.description: Statue of the first descendant of Nasus

fields.title: Pyke's Grave
fields.description: The burial spot of the Pirate drowned in sand

fields.title: Holy Temple
fields.description: A place to worship Shurima

fields.title: Centralis
fields.description: Shurima's neighboring Kingdom, home to the mighty

fields.title: Azir's Palace
fields.description: Grand Palace belonging to a descendant of Shurima

fields.title: Floating Pyramids
fields.description: Pyramids sitting high above the desert in Shurima

fields.title: Mountain Pass
fields.description: Mountain pass used to cross the boarder, blocked with a key locked gate

fields.title: Nefara's Necrocalis
fields.description: Hut laid out near the cemetary, used for Necromancy training

fields.title: Royal Palace
fields.description: Palace used by the King of Shurima

fields.title: Lake Shurima
fields.description: Lake surround most of Shurima, the waters shift from shallow to deep very quickly

fields.title: Shurima
fields.description: The Heavenly Kingdom of Shurima

fields.title: Velocatronic Rail Station
fields.description: Run down station that used to house the greatest train known to Shurima

fields.title: Voodou Lands
fields.description: Land owned by the Farmers of Shurima, plenty of desert fruit around to eat

fields.title: Water Gate
fields.description: Gate nested near the edge of the lake, to prevent flooding and the releasing of monstrous sea creatures

fields.title: Zayite Complex
fields.description: School specializing in life studies, and basic magics

fields.title: Tempest Forest
fields.description: Forest of cacti and high winds

fields.title: Mt. Targon
fields.description: The desolate mountain with the highest peak, Targon

fields.title: Fyron's Salt Flat
fields.description: House belonging to Fyron the Mage, imbued with magic and made of salt

fields.title: Adamantium Room
fields.description: There seem to be claw like slashes all over the room!

fields.title: American Room
fields.description: Captain America stuff is everywhere.

fields.title: Aquarium
fields.description: All of the walls are fish tanks. There seems to be an entrance through the floor to the tank.

fields.title: The Bullseye Room
fields.description: Hanging all around the room are targets that have been hit dead in the bullseye.

fields.title: Cerebro
fields.description: There is a weird helmet in the middle of this round room. Its like we are in a ball.

fields.title: Deadpool's Room
fields.description: There are little deadpool figurines everywhere. They all look to be dying though.

fields.title: Hawk Room
fields.description: There is a perch in the corner of the room.

fields.title: Ice
fields.description: Its so cold.

fields.title: Lightning
fields.description: This room seems to be charged with electricity. Don't touch the walls.

fields.title: Pitch Black
fields.description: Silence and darkness. You can't see anything in this room.

fields.title: The Rock
fields.description: Everywhere you look things are made of rock.

fields.title: Science Room
fields.description: It looks as though a monster tore out of this room.

fields.title: The Skull Room
fields.description: Guns and amo everywhere. There is a picture of a death's head skull on the wall.

fields.title: Small Room
fields.description: Everything in here is so tiny. Like it was made for ants.

fields.title: Smash Room
fields.description: You can see several Hulk shirts ripped apart. All the little Hulk figurines have been smashed into little bitty peaces.

fields.title: Stark's Room
fields.description: There are vast amounts of electronics all over this room.

fields.title: Tourch
fields.description: Everything is on fire.

fields.title: Web Room
fields.description: There are sticky webs all over this room.

fields.title: Suarward Dining
fields.description: Large, square dining room has mismatched wooden furniture.  The seating is cushioned.  The floor is stone. Overall has a quaint atmosphere.

fields.title: TallTail Chambers
fields.description: Small, rectangular bedroom with wooden funiture. Among the first things one notices walking in is muddy footprints on the floor.

fields.title: Starstrike Sanctuary
fields.description: This cramped, rectangular office has mismatched wooden, metal, and glass furniture, Upon entering one notices light from the heavens

fields.title: Grandwing Saloon
fields.description: Cramped, square, dim lit saloon. Broken glass covers the floor. There is a thick haze of smoke upon entering. Among the first things one notices walking in are a conspicuous stain on the floor

fields.title: Outcast Den
fields.description: Large, L-shaped bathroom screams death. Leave Quickly!

fields.title: Starfall Hideout
fields.description: Light is provided by wall lamps and a ceiling light. Among the first things one notices walking in are glitter footprints on the floor and a collection of action figures.

fields.title: Lightstorm Harbor
fields.description: Among the first things one notices walking in is photographs on the wall. Long ago this was a sailors palace

fields.title: Feather Nest
fields.description: A large, square bedroom. The floor is layered with shedded feathers. The first thing one notices upon entering is a broken clock on the wall

fields.title: Coldwar Hideaway
fields.description: The room is done in colors that remind you of Halloween and overall has a rustic look to it.  Among the first things one notices walking in are a crumpled paper

fields.title: Shadow Burrow
fields.description: Cold, and cluttered with spell books. Upon entering one feels a draft come from the window that chills the soul

fields.title: Miracle Dungeon
fields.description: This large kitchen is magical. Powered by one's own imagination

fields.title: skullblade_cave
fields.description: An average-sized cave, dark and mysterious. Sounds of flowing water come from deep within. Among entering bats fly out from everywhere.

fields.title: Thorn Nest
fields.description: Cramped office with matching wooden furniture. The room is done is such way it reminds one of a thorny nest

fields.title: Archkeep Sanctuary
fields.description: This spacious, bathroom is done in bold colors and overall has a quaint atmosphere.  Among the first things one notices walking in are a collection of knickknacks and many cosmetics strewn on the counter.

fields.title: Skyspell Haven
fields.description: Vintage theme in murky colors and overall has a retro look to it.  Among the first things one notices walking in is a barn star on the wall.

fields.title: Flower Retreat
fields.description: A mystical garden, that is home to many fairies, but beware the dragons below

fields.title: Blitz Cover
fields.description: Underground, yet well lit. Blitz Cover is a reminder of safety in these parts

fields.title: Mystery Lair
fields.description: The room of deja vu, beware!

fields.title: Gardners Garden
fields.description: This garden has grown the most lavish fruits and vegetables on the planet, look around you for fruits and vegetables.

fields.title: The Kings Tomb
fields.description: You've found the long-lost Kings Tomb! Press C to loot the tomb.

fields.title: Princess Peach castle
fields.description: You've arrived to Princess Peach Castle! See if she has anything for you.

fields.title: Bowsers Dungeon
fields.description: You're in Bowsers Dungeon, get what you can and get out of there!

fields.title: Toad Town
fields.description: Toad town is iconic, for housing some of the worlds biggest superstars. Look around and you might see Mario!

fields.title: Bonies Cabin
fields.description: Bonie welcomed you inside, for food.

fields.title: Goodnights Theatre
fields.description: Shhhh! The show is about to start.

fields.title: Yoshis Yoga Palace
fields.description: Sit down, close your eyes and find your inter zen.

fields.title: Sarasaland
fields.description: Queen Daisy has been awaiting you're arrival, check what you can do for her.

fields.title: Bowsers Kingdom
fields.description: Watch youself, you might be standing on lava!

fields.title: Warios Woods
fields.description: Warios Woods has plenty of organic resources, pack up what you can and head to the market!

fields.title: Rosalinas Land
fields.description: You've found the long-lost land of Princess Rosalina! The Lumas have left everything! Where could they be?

fields.title: Kooplings Shack
fields.description: find a bed and get some rest.

fields.title: Lumas Village
fields.description: Lumas village is known for its amazing sky at night, and great tradesmen. See if anyone wants to trade anything.

fields.title: Toads Boat
fields.description: Toad said he'd take you to a special Island. Do you want to go?

fields.title: Toads Island
fields.description: See what the people here have to offer.

fields.title: Marios Palace
fields.description: You've been selected to explore Marios palace.

fields.title: The Borg
fields.description: Prepare to be assimilated! Resistance is futile!

fields.title: The Enterprise
fields.description: Space: the final frontier. Boldy go!

fields.title: Planet Vulcan
fields.description: Live long and prosper. Just don't get emotional about it.

fields.title: The Replicator Room
fields.description: Order what you like. Picard recommneds: Tea, Earl Grey, hot!

fields.title: Alpha quadrant
fields.description: Ready to see the neighborhood? Make it so!

fields.title: The Transporter Room
fields.description: If things get freaky down there, just call out: Beam me up, Scotty! When you are ready to go down just call out 'Engage!'

fields.title: Stranded on Unknown Planet
fields.description: Did I tell you the one about Darmok and Jalad at Tanagra?

fields.title: The Holodeck
fields.description: Think of your wildest fantasy, and ypu're there. Try not to run into the walls. It can be a rude awakening.

fields.title: The Tribble Room
fields.description: The Trouble with Tribbles? Those cute little furry things? Why, they're no tribble a'tal.

fields.title: Romulan Warbird
fields.description: Get ready for battle! Death to the Cardassians!

fields.title: Shore Leave
fields.description: If you see Alice chasing a White Rabbit, tell her he went for a cup of tea.

fields.title: Planet Earth
fields.description: Earth inhabitants: Ugly bags of mostly water.

fields.title: Klingon Home Planet
fields.description: Get ready for some Gok. Best when the worms are alive and wriggling. Wash it down with a warm glass of Blood Wine.

fields.title: Jefferies Tube
fields.description: Just keep your head down and crawl low. Don't touch that pipe. It might be scaldingly hot. And if you touch the high power line, don't worry--no pain with instant death.

fields.title: Delta Quadrant
fields.description: Thought you were going on a short test run? No problem. Just forty years back to the Alpha Quadrant. Talk about a long distance Voyager.

fields.title: Pon Farr
fields.description: Thought you could just forget about it and it would go away? No way. Time to pair up my mate. May as well have some wild fun.

fields.title: The Neutral Zone
fields.description: Get out as quickly as you can. Breaking the treaty of the Neutral Zone is highly offensive. Watch out for that Romulan War bird. It's gunning for ya

fields.title: Bajoran Wormhole
fields.description: Thought the war on Bajora with the Cardassians was bad? Well, enjoy getting sucked into this Bajoran Wormhole. Maybe you will luck out and get to the other side and only have to face the Dominion.

fields.title: Baryon Sweep
fields.description: Such unfortunate timing my friend. You have managed to beam aboard a vessal undergoing a Baryon Sweep. Yes, any organic living matter will be neutralized when the Baryon Sweep gets to its position onboard the craft. Sure hope you are not organic.

fields.title: Cardassia Prime
fields.description: Lucky you. Very Festive times now on Cardassia Prime. Everyone is celebrating making war on Bajor. You are Bjoran you say? Uh oh!

fields.title: Borg Path
fields.description: A path headed down destruction adn chaos

fields.title: Desert Path
fields.description: Prepare yourself to see the wonders of Shurima

fields.title: Dirt Path
fields.description: Easy going path to a variety of adventures

fields.title: Randomizer Road
fields.description: A road that twists and turns beyond the will of fate

fields.title: Marvel Road
fields.description: The path to lead to your superhuman dreams

fields.title: Mushroom Road
fields.description: The road to meet Mario
